,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"珍惜眼前人，簡單嘅句子，有幾多人明白做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748394737c9e8d5f4ce83df6e316ff25508d28b2","tid":388273,"uid":38954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都有個，不過唔係死左，而係突然間消失左，都十幾年，果時我地成班人仲有講有笑一起玩，之後有一日突然間msn完全無on ,屋企搬埋，到呢幾年先知原來佢阿哥差人錢同埋佢失聰問題而怕我地朋友辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3246a84e2bc4e58ab97e4122c1563cd9abe92d","tid":388273,"uid":144248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"樓主節哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae08987fd0f056a731076241dd9af78b3eecaab","tid":388273,"uid":3581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都有個，不過唔係死左，而係突然間消失左，都十幾年，果時我地成班人仲有講有笑一起玩，之後有一日突然間msn完全無on ,屋企搬埋，到呢幾年先知原來佢阿哥差人錢同埋佢失聰問題而怕我地朋友辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都好啲唔係走左"},{"pid":"3272d73d3060cfb81dcfb170c729b1474d7e473a","tid":388273,"uid":24401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"我都有個朋友最幾個月跳左落黎走左<br />\n呢幾個月都好難過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲成日諗佢諗到失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7495872262e779e5409fe8d82249666f4aae73c9","tid":388273,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:49:31.000Z","msg":"好多巴絲都有同樣經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c47def78eccabed3d98b947fbf547cb2c16409","tid":388273,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote